Congratulations, we are pleased to notify you that you have been selected
from the WTO system network center to benefit sum of (US$690.000.00) from
COVID-19 ECONOMIC INJURY DISASTER GRANT TO HELP HUMANITY this July 2021
from WORLD TRADER CENTER ORGANIZATION DEPARTMENT OF THE TREASURY powered by
cash and wired transfer for Individuals, Businesses, Private Non-profits,
Homeowners and Renters.

You are advised to establish immediate contact and submit your benefit code
no which is (WTO721) together with a copy of your ID card to claim your
grant money via this branch bank Chief Payment officer e-mail address
below!!

E-mail: ubacontaccts@financier.com
Contact Person: Morris Thomas
Telephone: +22675908563

This will only take 24 hours of your time because all the arrangements are
already made for possible means of releasing the fund to you and 95% of the
total money will be donated to your community and any form of double claim
will lead to disqualification,

Once again congratulations from members and staff of the World trade center
organization. Take care of yourself and have a wonderful day.

Yours sincerely,
Mrs. Yoo Myung-hee
